The paper discusses the development of behaviour-based knowledge systems, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and robotics (cs.RO) as well as machine learning (cs.LG) and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the development of higher order cognitive capacities, which is related to neural networks (cs.NE).
